2ï¸âƒ£ Mini Project: Heart Disease Prediction (MiniProject.ipynb)
ğŸ“Œ Dataset: heart.csv (Heart Disease Dataset)
ğŸ“Œ Objective: Predict whether a patient has heart disease based on medical features.

Dataset Description:
Age: Age of the patient.
Sex: Male (M) or Female (F).
ChestPainType: Type of chest pain (ATA, NAP, ASY, etc.).
RestingBP: Resting blood pressure.
Cholesterol: Serum cholesterol levels.
MaxHR: Maximum heart rate achieved.
HeartDisease: Target variable (1 = Disease, 0 = No Disease).
Key Features:
Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA) using Seaborn & Matplotlib.
Feature correlation heatmap to identify important attributes.
Random Forest Classifier for heart disease prediction.
Performance evaluation using accuracy scores.


